sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer as Customer App
    participant WS as WebSocket Server
    participant Backend as Backend API
    participant DelayService as Delay Detection
    participant CompService as Compensation Service
    participant DB as Database
    
    Note over DelayService: Runs every 2 minutes
    DelayService->>DB: Check all in-transit orders
    DB-->>DelayService: Order #12345 ETA exceeded
    
    DelayService->>DelayService: Calculate new ETA
    DelayService->>DB: Update order status to "delayed"
    DelayService->>WS: Broadcast delay event
    
    WS->>Customer: {"event": "delivery_delayed", "data": {...}}
    Customer->>Customer: Show yellow warning banner
    Customer->>Customer: Display new ETA: 45 min
    
    Note over Customer: Customer sees delay warning
    
    alt Customer waits (no action)
        Customer->>Customer: Continue tracking
    else Customer views options
        Customer->>Customer: Navigate to DelayOptionsScreen
        alt Customer cancels order
            Customer->>Backend: POST /orders/:id/cancel
            Backend->>DB: Update status to "cancelled"
            Backend->>CompService: Initiate full refund
            Backend-->>Customer: Cancellation confirmed
        else Customer contacts support
            Customer->>Backend: POST /support/tickets
            Backend-->>Customer: Support ticket created
        end
    end
    
    Note over DelayService: Check if delay > 30 min
    DelayService->>DelayService: Delay is 35 minutes
    DelayService->>CompService: Apply compensation
    CompService->>DB: Add 500 FCFA credit
    CompService->>WS: Broadcast compensation event
    
    WS->>Customer: {"event": "compensation_applied", "data": {...}}
    Customer->>Customer: Show green compensation banner
    Customer->>Customer: Update order total
    
    Note over Customer: Positive experience recovery!

